{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"calcMode","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/calcMode","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n\n<p>이 속성은 애니메이션의 interpolation 모드를 지정합니다. 기본 모드는 linear 이지만 속성이 linear interpolation을 지원하지 않으면(예: 문자열의 경우) calcMode 속성이 무시되고 discrete interpolation이 사용됩니다.&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_context","title":"Usage context","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Categories</th>\n   <td>Animation value attribute</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td>discrete | linear | paced | spline</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Normative document</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/animate.html#CalcModeAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"discrete\">discrete</dt>\n <dd>이것은 애니메이션 함수가 interpolation 없이&nbsp;하나의 값에서 다음 값으로 점프하도록 지정합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"linear\">linear</dt>\n <dd>값 사이의 단순한 linear interpolation은 애니메이션 함수를 계산하는데 사용됩니다. <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateMotion\"><code>&lt;animateMotion&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>의 경우를 제외하고는 이것은 기본 값입니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"paced\">paced</dt>\n <dd>Defines interpolation to produce an even pace of change across the animation. This is only supported for values that define a linear numeric range, and for which some notion of \"distance\" between points can be calculated (e.g. position, width, height, etc.). If paced is specified, any <code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/keyTimes\">keyTimes</a></code> or <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/keySplines\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">keySplines (en-US)</a></code> will be ignored. For <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateMotion\"><code>&lt;animateMotion&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, this is the default value.</dd>\n <dt id=\"spline\">spline</dt>\n <dd>cubic Bézier spline에 정의된 시간 함수에 따라&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/values\">values</a></code> 목록의 한 값에서 다음 값으로 interpolation 합니다. spline의 점(point)은&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/keyTimes\">keyTimes</a></code> 속성에 정의되고, &nbsp;각 간격의 제어점은 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/keySplines\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">keySplines (en-US)</a></code> 속성에 정의됩니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"Elements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>다음 요소에서 calcMode 속성을 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animate&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animateColor&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateMotion\"><code>&lt;animateMotion&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateTransform\"><code>&lt;animateTransform&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Usage context","id":"usage_context"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"Elements","id":"elements"}],"summary":"« SVG Attribute reference home","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"calcMode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"calcMode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/svg/attribute/calcmode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/svg/attribute/calcmode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG Attribute reference"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/calcMode","title":"calcMode"}],"pageTitle":"calcMode - SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics | MDN","noIndexing":false}}